    "The illegibility aspect of handwriting due to the defect in understanding of space results in spatial dysgraphia.",
    "Suitable line/ word segmentation techniques [115] can be utilized to observe and compare the line as well as the word spacing.",
    "Further, document analysis algorithms [49] serve to identify dysgraphic characteristics such as skewed writing, irregular writing size, etc.As a result, the framework was developed and implemented at Qatar University to create a new multimodal database for the diagnosis and assistance evaluation of dysgraphia in students.",
